WEBVTT

0
00:00:02.469 --> 00:00:06.462
I'm Peppa Pig. This is
my little brother, George.

1
00:00:07.173 --> 00:00:08.367
This is Mummy Pig.

2
00:00:09.476 --> 00:00:10.738
And this is Daddy Pig.

3
00:00:13.179 --> 00:00:14.168
Peppa pig.

4
00:00:19.052 --> 00:00:20.986
New Shoes!

5
00:00:25.125 --> 00:00:26.990
Peppa and George have been
playing in the garden.

6
00:00:31.131 --> 00:00:33.565
Peppa, Where are your shoes?

7
00:00:34.401 --> 00:00:36.494
Oh, I've lost them.

8
00:00:36.903 --> 00:00:38.894
Well, I'm sure We can find them.

9
00:00:39.773 --> 00:00:42.003
Maybe We should try the garden?

10
00:00:42.642 --> 00:00:43.700
Yes!

11
00:00:46.413 --> 00:00:48.210
Everyone is looking for
Peppa's shoes.

12
00:00:49.649 --> 00:00:51.207
Mummy Pig is looking
in the flowerbed.

13
00:00:52.085 --> 00:00:53.518
Peppa's shoes are not there.

14
00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:54.516
Oh!

15
00:00:55.155 --> 00:00:56.713
Daddy Pig is looking
in the Wheelbarrow.

16
00:00:57.023 --> 00:00:58.786
Peppa's shoes are not there.

17
00:00:59.292 --> 00:01:00.156
Oh!

18
00:01:01.594 --> 00:01:03.289
Peppa and George look
in the flowerpots.

19
00:01:03.663 --> 00:01:05.654
Peppa's shoes are not there, either.

20
00:01:06.099 --> 00:01:07.225
Oh! Oh!

21
00:01:07.867 --> 00:01:09.459
We've looked everywhere,

22
00:01:09.736 --> 00:01:11.727
but We can't find Peppa's shoes!

23
00:01:12.172 --> 00:01:13.605
Peppa's shoes are lost.

24
00:01:14.174 --> 00:01:16.540
Now I haven't got any shoes
to Wear.

25
00:01:17.243 --> 00:01:20.110
Poor Peppa. Your shoes Were
getting a bit old...

26
00:01:20.880 --> 00:01:22.370
We'll buy you a new pair!

27
00:01:22.682 --> 00:01:24.741
Can my new shoes be red, Mummy?

28
00:01:24.984 --> 00:01:26.178
Of course, they can.

29
00:01:26.553 --> 00:01:29.818
George! I'm going to have
new red shoes!

30
00:01:34.561 --> 00:01:37.394
Mummy Pig and Peppa are
at Miss Rabbit's shoe shop.

31
00:01:38.198 --> 00:01:39.130
Hello, Miss Rabbit.

32
00:01:39.332 --> 00:01:40.264
Hello, Mummy Pig.

33
00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:42.764
We Would like to buy some new
shoes for Peppa, please.

34
00:01:43.403 --> 00:01:44.836
Red Shoes!

35
00:01:45.138 --> 00:01:47.834
Oh I'm sure We can find you
some Iovely new shoes, Peppa!

36
00:01:48.007 --> 00:01:50.134
Red ones, please.

37
00:01:50.477 --> 00:01:52.342
Of course, red ones.

38
00:01:53.146 --> 00:01:59.847
Wow! New red shoes!

39
00:02:05.024 --> 00:02:06.855
George and Daddy Pig are
playing draughts.

40
00:02:08.027 --> 00:02:10.518
Oh, Well done, George.

41
00:02:10.663 --> 00:02:11.527
Daddy! Daddy!

42
00:02:12.799 --> 00:02:15.529
Look at my new shoes!
They are red!

43
00:02:16.169 --> 00:02:18.433
I say! They are red.

44
00:02:18.738 --> 00:02:20.672
Mummy, do you like
my new shoes?

45
00:02:20.940 --> 00:02:23.932
Yes, Peppa, they make you
look very smart.

46
00:02:24.677 --> 00:02:26.872
George, do you like my new shoes?

47
00:02:29.315 --> 00:02:31.044
Everyone likes Peppa's new shoes.

48
00:02:31.751 --> 00:02:33.946
I like my new shoes so much.

49
00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:36.384
I don't Want to ever take them off.

50
00:02:39.893 --> 00:02:41.190
It is bath time.

51
00:02:41.694 --> 00:02:42.820
Peppa Wants to keep her
new shoes on,

52
00:02:43.062 --> 00:02:44.324
even for her bath.

53
00:02:48.568 --> 00:02:49.694
Peppa is in her pajamas.

54
00:02:49.969 --> 00:02:51.630
She still has her new shoes on.

55
00:02:55.074 --> 00:02:57.838
Peppa even Wants to Wear
her new shoes in bed!

56
00:02:58.144 --> 00:02:59.475
Peppa, are you sure

57
00:02:59.579 --> 00:03:00.841
you don't Want to take your shoes off?

58
00:03:01.147 --> 00:03:03.707
I don't Want to ever take
my new shoes off, Mummy.

59
00:03:04.417 --> 00:03:07.409
Very Well. Goodnight, Peppa and George.

60
00:03:10.924 --> 00:03:13.859
Goodnight, Mummy!
Goodnight, Daddy

61
00:03:14.594 --> 00:03:16.585
Goodnight, my little piggies!

62
00:03:21.301 --> 00:03:22.734
It has been raining all night

63
00:03:23.102 --> 00:03:24.160
and now the garden is very Wet.

64
00:03:25.939 --> 00:03:27.236
Mummy Pig is Wearing her boots.

65
00:03:27.674 --> 00:03:29.005
Daddy Pig is Wearing his boots.

66
00:03:29.609 --> 00:03:31.372
George is Wearing his boots.

67
00:03:32.178 --> 00:03:34.510
Peppa is still Wearing
her new red shoes.

68
00:03:36.816 --> 00:03:38.613
George is going to play
in the Wet grass.

69
00:03:41.521 --> 00:03:44.183
Oh, dear. Peppa loves
playing in the Wet grass,

70
00:03:44.457 --> 00:03:46.118
but she doesn't Want to get
her new shoes Wet.

71
00:03:46.693 --> 00:03:49.457
I can't play in the
Wet grass, George.

72
00:03:49.896 --> 00:03:50.624
Oh.

73
00:03:53.533 --> 00:03:55.194
George loves jumping in
muddy puddles.

74
00:03:57.537 --> 00:03:59.334
Peppa loves jumping in
puddles,

75
00:03:59.539 --> 00:04:01.336
but she doesn't Want
to get her new shoes muddy.

76
00:04:01.975 --> 00:04:02.771
Oh.

77
00:04:03.910 --> 00:04:06.037
Mummy and Daddy love jumping
up and down in muddy puddles!

78
00:04:07.046 --> 00:04:08.980
Everyone likes jumping in muddy puddles!

79
00:04:12.051 --> 00:04:13.040
Where is Peppa going?

80
00:04:17.056 --> 00:04:18.648
Peppa is putting on her boots!

81
00:04:29.369 --> 00:04:30.927
Wheeeeee!

82
00:04:32.572 --> 00:04:34.506
lf you jump in muddy puddles,

83
00:04:34.807 --> 00:04:36.502
you must Wear your boots!

